Nawala sa isang upuan.

00:28:07.035 --> 00:28:08.235
Sayang naman.

00:28:08.555 --> 00:28:09.676
Simula nung

00:28:09.676 --> 00:28:11.596
masyado ka bang naging transactional sa akin?

00:28:11.596 --> 00:28:12.235
